---
title: Duck Cassoulet with Toasted Ciabatta
description: Duck can be used in so many delicious ways, sometimes it's hard to know where to begin. This decadent Southern French dish could be the perfect introduction to this wonderful protein! We let the duck shine by using everything duck breast has to offer, but it's the combination of beautifully seared meat and a luxurious buttery bean stew that makes this dish a winner.  Happy eating!
